title: Lucy Hale and her dog, Elvis, celebrated NYE together, and it was so precious
text:
Lucy Hale and her dog, Elvis, celebrated NYE together, and it was so precious We absolutely love Lucy Hale. The only thing we love more than Lucy Hale is probably Lucy Hale and Elvis, her beloved pup. Hale and Elvis are seriously precious AF , and their selfies always make us smile oh-so-big. So we were happy to see that the adorable duo was able to wrap up the new year together. Seriously, find a more #goals pairing than Lucy Hale and her dog, our ultimate BFF inspo. It’s impossible!
Honestly, our favorite NYE duo is Lucy Hale and Elvis. They’re so, so cute. A photo posted by Lucy Hale (@lucyhale) on Jan 1, 2017 at 1:14am PST 
She captioned the post,
“Tonight was unrea . Happy new year everyone from me and my main man Elvis!” ICYMI, Lucy Hale spent most of New Year’s Eve hosting the Rockin’ Eve event in New Orleans. A photo posted by Lucy Hale (@lucyhale) on Dec 31, 2016 at 2:56pm PST 
She was working her butt off, and we’re so proud of her! We know this was a big, big moment for Lucy. A photo posted by Lucy Hale (@lucyhale) on Dec 30, 2016 at 6:23pm PST 
‘ And, OMG, she looked *so* beautiful! We totally dig her New Year’s Eve look. A photo posted by Lucy Hale (@lucyhale) on Dec 31, 2016 at 6:44pm PST 

She’s definitely ready for 2017, and we look forward to even more style inspo. A photo posted by Lucy Hale (@lucyhale) on Dec 31, 2016 at 8:09pm PST 
But we know Lucy is always happy to wrap up her days beside Elvis. A photo posted by Lucy Hale (@lucyhale) on Dec 19, 2016 at 7:20am PST 
They’re so precious. A . A photo posted by Lucy Hale (@lucyhale) on Nov 28, 2016 at 10:38am PST 
Thanks for the mom-and-pup goals, Lucy Hale and Elvis! We heart you two so much.
